            <title>Oatmeal 1.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.1</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Meeting Auto-Detection:</strong> Get notified when a call starts — tap to record instantly.</li>
                    <li><strong>Pause &amp; Resume:</strong> Pause recording mid-meeting and pick back up.</li>
                    <li><strong>Auto-Updates:</strong> Oatmeal now checks for updates automatically via Sparkle.</li>
                    <li><strong>Background Model Loading:</strong> Speech models download on first launch instead of blocking your first meeting.</li>
                    <li><strong>UI fixes:</strong> Sidebar layout fixed, auto-selects most recent meeting on launch.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
